com.pb.sawdust.util.sql.wrappers

Class WrappedResultSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pb.sawdust.util.sql.wrappers.WrappedResultSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.sql.ResultSet, java.sql.Wrapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IsolatedResultSet

    public class WrappedResultSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.sql.ResultSet
    The ResultSetWrapper class provides a wrapper class for java.sql.ResultSet implementations which can be used as a convenience to selectively override one or more of ResultSet's methods. This class implements the ResultSet interface by passing through all of its methods to the wrapped implementaion. Thus, by wrapping an implementation in this class and overriding one or more of this class' methods, the effect is to override the method(s) in the implementation.
